Package org.cesta.grammars.java

Java grammars.

See: Description

Package org.cesta.grammars.java Description

Java grammars.

The package contains:

  • combined lexer and parser grammar Java.g
  • tree parser grammar JavaTreeParser.g
  • transformation grammars "TransformationName"Parser.g using the tokens from Java.g and inheriting AST from JavaTreeParser.g
